original_title: Joan Jett & The Blackhearts - Live in Dortmund
overview: Joan Jett & The Blackhearts support I Love Rock 'n Roll with a 30-minute concert filmed in Dortmund, Germany in 1982 and aired on ZDF RockPop in Concert.  Setlist:  01. Intro by Fritz Egner  02. (I'm Gonna) Run Away  03. Wooly Bully  04. Victim of Circumstance  05. I Love Rock 'N Roll  06. Nag  07. Crimson and Clover  08. Do You Wanna Touch Me  09. Shout
title: Joan Jett & The Blackhearts - Live in Dortmund
